iPerhaps one day in the distant future our silly thoughts and ideas		gopher.black	70
iwill be gathered together, chopped up, and turned into something		gopher.black	70
inew and unexpected. Maybe we'll all sit in a virtual cabinet for		gopher.black	70
idecades first. Maybe some of it will fade away or be lost, but		gopher.black	70
iI think there's a good chance for resiliency. Our stuff is mostly		gopher.black	70
itext, after all, and that doesn't take up much space.		gopher.black	70
